            img(style='max-width: 90%; max-height: 250px; margin: 5px;', src='https://en.#{ExtraData.domain}/uploads/files/7/8/4/5/d/7845d9193a47c30a3463ad9d5665250c.jpg', alt)
        p Ullam porro ipsum officia ducimus cum beatae corrupti quia adipisci enim dolores blanditiis reiciendis, nam consequuntur animi ex debitis impedit sit a, sapiente praesentium sed laudantium. Nostrum debitis explicabo in.
